        "description": "An observational study in which hemolysis data were collected from a mock circulatory loop operating under five pre-specified CPB flow-speed combinations. No independent variable manipulation was performed by the investigators; operating conditions were set according to standard clinical perfusion protocols and data were recorded as encountered. Measurements included plasma-free hemoglobin concentration, hematocrit, and derived RH index values across three replicate runs per operating point.",
